snippet.title: ASKA Announcement Trailer | Closed Alpha November 2022
snippet.description:
Wishlist now and sign up for closed Alpha: http://playaska.com/ 

Sand Sailor Studio are excited to unveil the new Viking themed open-world survival tribe builder, ASKA.

Join the tribe:
ASKA Discord: https://discord.gg/dfBKTrCKcH
ASKA Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/askathegame/
ASKA Tiktok: https://www.tiktok.com/@askathegame 
ASKA Twitter: https://twitter.com/ASKAthegame
